name: Tedesis
public_notice: Tedesis has migrated from Ethereum to Binance Smart Chain

description.en: The Tedesis system and its Blockchain, allow to authenticate and guarantee the authenticity of all types of online content. In order to fight against frauds, misappropriations, scams, identity theft and fakes news. The Tedesis cryptocurrency is deflationary, for each transaction carried out, 5% of the funds of the transaction are redistributed to the holders.
